title: SCHITEC Dog Squeaky Toy, 6 PCS Latex Bouncy Egg Balls with Squeaker for Puppy Small Pet Dogs, Soft Rubber Sound Toys for Interactive Fetch Play
features: Fun Squeaky Dog Ball Toys: The squeaky dog ball are bouncy and have fun egg shape that dogs love to chase. With built-in voice device, they make squeaky sound easily when dogs bite or squeeze them. The funny squeak can attract your dog's interest and give them a lot of fun

Safe and Durable: Made of natural latex and no stuffing, the latex squeaky dog toys for small dogs are non-toxic and safe for your pets to chew and play. This high-quality material makes them smooth, good elasticity and easy to clean

Interactive Play Dog Balls : The soft squeaky balls are great for gentle chewing, chasing and fetching indoor and outdoor. It's perfect for interactive games to enhance your relationship with your pets

6 Pack Colorful Toys with Cute Faces for Small Dogs: 1.7''x1.7''x2.3'' cute egg balls, great gift for Chihuahua, Shih Tzu, Teddy, Pug, Yorkshire Terrier, Poodle, Dachshund and other small dogs less than 11kg (24.25lb). Designed with 6 funny smiley faces and painted in different colors, the unique toys are perfect gift for your pet
For Puppy & Small Dogs: Package includes 6pcs soft latex squeaky dog toys. We recommend supervised play to help toys last longer and most importantly keep your pal safe
description: Product Description Product Details Inner Squeaker The squeaker inside gives out an attractive sound easily when squeezed, great for fun and entertainment. Premium Material Made of natural latex, safe for pups to chew and play. Soft and bouncy balls are good for your pup’s teeth and also easy to clean. Perfect for Small Dogs The best gift for Chihuahua, Shih Tzu, Teddy, Pug, Yorkshire Terrier, Poodle, Dachshund and other small dogs less than 11kg (24.25lb). Fun Squeaky Toy Squeaky toys can attract dogs to chew and squeeze, which makes your dog excited and reduce boredom. Interactive Play Soft and bouncy balls are easy to fetch and throw, your dog will love playing tossing and fetching with it. Suitable for Water Games Lightweight design allows the toys to float in water, great for interactive play at the beach, lake or pool. Squeaky Doy Toy Set Material: Natural Latex Size: 1.7 x 1.7 x 2.3 inches Package Include: 6 PCS Squeaky Balls with assorted patterns Warm tips ● These toys are suitable for small and medium dogs. Large dogs are too destructive and may tear the balls. ● Dogs should be supervised while playing with toys, and don't let your pet swallow the toys. ● It is designed as a fetch toy rather than a chew toy, please teach your pets how to play.
